## Limitations

This report is based on available data and literature up to October 2023. The findings are subject to the limitations of the sources used, including potential biases in reporting and the dynamic nature of climate change impacts. Additionally, the report does not cover all possible impacts of climate change on tourism, focusing instead on the most prominent issues identified in the sources. Further research is needed to explore mitigation strategies and long-term adaptations for the tourism industry.